## Contact Lookup & Relationship Management

**When looking up a contact, preparing for a meeting, or managing relationships:**
Use the `digital-brain` skill — contacts live in `~/.claude/skills/digital-brain/network/contacts.jsonl`

**When looking up org structure or terminology:**
See `org-context.md` (create this with your own org info)

